channel.description: ive been tryin all day on www.no-ip.com and every ip i make for my server i get the eroor message it works perfectly without an ip but no one can get on so when i make an ip i compile then run and still get error message if you have any idea on what to do plz respond....

item.title: I just created a server of my own and i cant get an ip for it
item.dc:creator: @Pure_pk1 Puré_pk
item.description:
@Pure_pk1 wrote:

You can go to no-ip.org. after that u can go to Hamachi and Download that. but if you Forward the port you
can add it to Moparscape server status (:

i use the Simple way.

Downloading Ham

Downloading Source

Compile&Run

ps: in the ham Network you’ll see your IP.

Then if want other players join say:

Ham net: Your net name

Ham pass: your Pass

server port: 4395 or 5555 (You can Change it in the Server.java in your Source.

ip: Your Ham ip

My server:

Ham Net: Moparscape4ever

Ham pass: 5555

Server Port: 43954

Ip: 5.92.108.100

Thx Puré_PK!
